&uuml;&yacute;tgetmek bilen lukman &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;ni&#328; &ouml;smegine
baha berip biler.&nbsp;Synag wagtynda agyry, &ccedil;i&#351;me derejesine
baglylykda &yacute;um&#351;ak rahatsyzlykdan agyr agyrylara &ccedil;enli
bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Rektal barlag 15 sekuntdan k&ouml;p dowam
etme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

