alkogolly i&ccedil;gilerden &ccedil;ykarmak maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Has k&ouml;p suw
i&ccedil;i&#328;.&nbsp;Birn&auml;&ccedil;e g&ouml;zlegde sink ba&yacute;
i&yacute;mitleri i&yacute;mek maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r: et, de&#328;iz
&ouml;n&uuml;mleri, ysmanak, hoz, &yacute;um&#351;ak pe&yacute;nir.</span></p>

