color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Uteiti &yacute;a-da dowamly bakterial prostatiti&#328;
bejergisinde&nbsp;<b>antibiotik bejergisi&nbsp;</b>zerurdyr.&nbsp;N&auml;sagda
serho&#351;lygy&#328; agyr alamatlary bar bolsa, dermanlary&#328; damar
damarlaryny kabul etmegi zerur bolup biler.&nbsp;Aciti bakterial prostatitde
antibiotik bejergisini&#328; dowamlylygy adat&ccedil;a 14 g&uuml;nden
ge&ccedil;me&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Dowamly bakterial prostatitde bejergini&#328;
uzak m&ouml;hletli bolmagy - antibiotikleri kabul etmegi&#328; 4-8
hepdesi.&nbsp;Dowamly infeksi&yacute;any bejermek, bakteri&yacute;alary&#328;
k&ouml;plen&ccedil; antibiotiklere gar&#351;y durmagy we indiki dermanlara
ge&ccedil;megi bilen kynla&#351;dyryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Antibiotik
sa&yacute;lamak pe&#351;ew medeni&yacute;etini&#328; netijelerine
esaslan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Agyry we &ccedil;i&#351;megi azaltmak &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>steroid
&yacute;okan&ccedil;lyga gar&#351;y dermanlar&nbsp;</b>bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;N&auml;sagy&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;y agyr bolsa, plan&#351;et, rektal &ccedil;aklamalar we
damar g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde bolup biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dowamly abacterial
prostatiti&#328; (dowamly &ccedil;anaklyk sindromyny) bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulany&#328;:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>alfa-blokatorlar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
my&#351;sany&#328; &auml;he&#328;ine t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;n, prostata we
&ouml;t haltasyny&#328; my&#351;salaryny gow&#351;atmaga k&ouml;mek
ed&yacute;&auml;n dermanlar, &#351;e&yacute;lelik bilen pe&#351;ewi
gowulandyr&yacute;ar;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>5-alfa reduktaz ingibitorlary&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- bu
dermanlar testosterony has i&#351;je&#328; gormona
&ouml;w&uuml;r&yacute;&auml;n fermenti blokla&yacute;ar, bu prostata
m&auml;zini&#328; gi&#328;elmegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
al&yacute;ar;&nbsp;bu dermanlar esasan o&#328;at prostat adenomasyny bejermekde
ulanyl&yacute;ar, &yacute;&ouml;ne k&ouml;p sanly g&ouml;zlegler dowamly
abacterial prostatiti&#328; bejergisinde netijeliligini subut etdi;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>fosfodiesteraz-5 ingibitorlary&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>esasan
erektil disfunksi&yacute;any bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar;&nbsp;Dowamly &ccedil;anak agyry sindromyny&#328; alamatlaryny
a&yacute;yrmakda t&auml;sirli bolandygy subut edildi;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>antibakterial dermanlar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
bakterial hroniki prostatit bilen ge&ccedil;irilen analizlerde
bakteri&yacute;alary&#328; tapylma&yacute;andygyna garamazdan, lukmanlar
antibiotikleri &ccedil;&auml;kli wagt &uuml;&ccedil;in, d&ouml;rt hepdeden
k&ouml;p dowam etmezligi tab&#351;yr&yacute;arlar;&nbsp;Bu strategi&yacute;a,
k&auml;bir alamatlara bakteri&yacute;a &yacute;oka&#351;masy seb&auml;pli
d&auml;l-de, &ccedil;i&#351;me seb&auml;p bolsa-da, k&auml;bir erkeklere
k&ouml;mek edip biler;&nbsp;k&auml;bir antibiotikleri&#328;
&ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y h&auml;si&yacute;etleri bar, &yacute;&ouml;ne
steroid &yacute;okan&ccedil;lyga gar&#351;y dermanlardan tapawutly
i&#351;le&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Prostat massaagey&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>prostatiti&#328; alamatlaryny
a&yacute;yryp biler, &yacute;&ouml;ne bejergini&#328; bu
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ini&#328; t&auml;siri indi has &#351;&uuml;bheli we
halkara lukman&ccedil;ylyk g&ouml;zleglerini&#328; k&ouml;p&uuml;si tarapyndan
tassyklanma&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Dowamly abacterial prostatitde&nbsp;<b>akupunktur&nbsp;</b>gowy
netijeleri g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;Akupunktur endogen
opi&yacute;atlary&#328; b&ouml;l&uuml;nip &ccedil;ykmagyna k&ouml;mek
ed&yacute;&auml;r we &#351;e&yacute;lelik bilen my&#351;sa
s&uuml;&yacute;&uuml;mlerind&auml;ki agyryny we dartgynlygy
&yacute;e&#328;ille&#351;dir&yacute;&auml;r di&yacute;ip
hasaplan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki
amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly
&yacute;agda&yacute;lar bar bolsa, hirurgi&yacute;a zerur bolup biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Uteiti pe&#351;ew
saklananda pe&#351;ew kateteri go&yacute;ul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Eger pe&#351;ew
&ccedil;ykary&#351; &yacute;oly bo&yacute;un&ccedil;a (pe&#351;ew
&ccedil;ykary&#351; &yacute;oly arkaly) edip bolma&yacute;an bolsa, onda
kateter ultrases barlagyny&#328; a&#351;agyndaky suprapubik sebite
kesil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Prostatany&#328; absesi
(yiringli &ccedil;i&#351;me) hirurgiki a&ccedil;ylmagyny we bo&#351;lugy&#328;
drenajyny talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328;
hilini dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>I&#351;je&#328;
bejergini gutarandan so&#328;, lukman i&yacute;mitlenmek we beden
i&#351;je&#328;ligi barada maslahat berer.&nbsp;Py&yacute;ada
&yacute;&ouml;remek, suwda &yacute;&uuml;zmek, tennis, lykiada typmak we
be&yacute;lekiler &yacute;aly aerobika ma&#351;klary dowamly prostatiti&#328;
alamatlaryny ep-esli derejede &yacute;e&#328;ille&#351;dir&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Aciti pe&#351;ewi&#328; saklanmagy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, agyr
agyry bilen bilelikde derrew lukman&ccedil;ylyk gaty&#351;magyny talap
ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu b&ouml;wrek &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligine, sepsise,
&yacute;agny &auml;hli organlary&#328; we ulgamlary&#328; i&#351;ini
boz&yacute;an ulgamla&yacute;yn &ccedil;i&#351;me reaksi&yacute;asyna
seb&auml;p bolup biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Uteiti sistit&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, bakteri&yacute;alary&#328;
girmegi seb&auml;pli &ouml;t&nbsp;<b>haltany&#328;&nbsp;</b>&ccedil;i&#351;megi.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Uteiti pi&yacute;elonefrit&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>b&ouml;wreklerde
&yacute;okan&ccedil; we &ccedil;i&#351;me bolup dur&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Prostat absesi&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, prostata
m&auml;zini&#328; yiringli &ccedil;i&#351;mesi.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtik
iri&#328; bilen doldurylan bo&#351;lukdyr.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki
gaty&#351;magy talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Dowamly prostatit&nbsp;<b>&ouml;nelgesizlige&nbsp;</b>elt&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;-
prostatadaky uzak wagtlap dowam ed&yacute;&auml;n &ccedil;i&#351;me prosesi
sperma hereketine t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;r we eger seminal kanallar
gatna&#351;sa, e&yacute;akul&yacute;asi&yacute;a wagtynda sperma
&ccedil;ykaryly&#351;y bozul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Teklipler, adat&ccedil;a,
sagdyn durmu&#351; &yacute;&ouml;relgesini&#328; umumy d&uuml;zg&uuml;nlerine
gabat gel&yacute;&auml;r: sagdyn we d&uuml;rli i&yacute;mitlenmek,
bedenterbi&yacute;e i&#351;je&#328;ligi, howpsuz
jyns.&nbsp;A&yacute;ratynlyklaryndan di&#328;e a&#351;a ysly, bur&ccedil;ly
i&yacute;mitleri&#328; ret edilmegini we anal jyns d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde goraga
a&yacute;ratyn &uuml;ns bermegi m&uuml;mkin.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Aciti bakterial
prostatiti&#328; ilkinji &yacute;agda&yacute;yny&#328; &ccedil;aklamasy gowy,
esasy zat ba&#351;arnykly antibiotik bejergisini&#328; wagtynda
bellenilmegi.&nbsp;Dowamly prostatiti&#328; &ccedil;aklamasy esasan o&#328;a
seb&auml;p bolan seb&auml;be baglydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Prostatit prostat
m&auml;zini&#328; d&ouml;remek howpuny &yacute;okarlandyrma&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Aciti prostatiti&#328; dowamly kesele &ouml;wr&uuml;lmek
&auml;htimallygym n&auml;me?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Prostata g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in yzygiderli
barlaglar ge&ccedil;irmelimi?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Prostatit &uuml;&ccedil;in sportu&#328; ha&yacute;sy
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri kontrendikedir?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Jynsy i&#351;je&#328;lik, prostatit keseline n&auml;hili
t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;r?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Alkogol i&ccedil;gileri keseli&#328; gidi&#351;ine n&auml;hili
t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;r?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Bejergi usullary ha&yacute;sylar?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ulanylan
edebi&yacute;aty&#328; sanawy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

